aretz.com/jewish/2024-07-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jewish-youth-from-around-europe-write-about-their-lives-now-and-85-years-ago/00000190-a26f-da1a-adf0-a6ff4cb40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的暴躁表演利用特朗普的暗杀企图来削减以色列总检察长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-petulant-theatrics-leverage-trump-assassination-attempt-to-axe-israels-ag/00000190-b537-df08-a9fe-f5f7f92d0000</link><description>人质？伤亡？战争？以色列内阁用了两个小时的时间讨论了总理的悲惨命运，总理利用受害者的叙述并推动解雇目中无人的总检察长</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 08:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-petulant-theatrics-leverage-trump-assassination-attempt-to-axe-israels-ag/00000190-b537-df08-a9fe-f5f7f92d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙的暗杀行动是否终止了人质交易？答案就在卡塔尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/did-israels-assassination-attempt-kill-the-hostage-deal-the-answer-is-in-qatar/00000190-b2e1-d9c3-ad99-bfe351500000</link><description>以色列官员认为，在加沙刺杀哈马斯二号人物的企图将有助于谈判，但有人担心辛瓦尔将继续存在，甚至以他的生命为代价；暗杀企图失败后，特朗普的预期激增可能给内塔尼亚胡带来两个不同的挑战</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 03:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/did-israels-assassination-attempt-kill-the-hostage-deal-the-answer-is-in-qatar/00000190-b2e1-d9c3-ad99-bfe351500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称与哈马斯的人质谈判仍在继续；以色列国防军负责人表示，协议是“道义上的当务之急”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article-live/israel-says-hostage-talks-with-hamas-continue-idf-chief-israel-is-creating-pressure/00000190-b427-d3c7-ab94-beef50bb0000</link><description>英国海事机构收到也门荷台达西南部事件的报告 ■ 以色列官员表示，在穆罕默德·代夫遭暗杀后，与哈马斯的人质谈判将继续进行，哈马斯给出了复杂的信息 ■ 在中部拉姆拉附近的汽车撞击袭击中，四名士兵受伤，其中两人伤势严重以色列 ■ 以色列国防军证实哈马斯指挥官汗·尤尼斯被杀 ■ 据报道，以色列国防军周日袭击加沙近东救济工程处学校，造成 15 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 02:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article-live/israel-says-hostage-talks-with-hamas-continue-idf-chief-israel-is-creating-pressure/00000190-b427-d3c7-ab94-beef50bb0000</guid></item><item><title>Bibi，旅行社；内塔尼亚胡如何使用控制柜的所有付费旅行费用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/bibi-the-travel-agent-how-netanyahu-uses-all-expenses-paid-trips-to-control-cabinet/00000190-b289-d9c3-ad99-bfabde330000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 00:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/bibi-the-travel-agent-how-netanyahu-uses-all-expenses-paid-trips-to-control-cabinet/00000190-b289-d9c3-ad99-bfabde330000</guid></item><item><title>在哈马斯混乱的声明中，以色列称人质谈判仍在继续</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/amid-confused-hamas-statements-israel-says-hostage-talks-continue/00000190-b2e3-d7ee-af9c-ffeb57d40000</link><description>主要障碍仍然是内塔尼亚胡要求防止武装武装分子在以色列国防军撤军后返回加沙地带北部。国外消息来源对接下来发生的事情的估计似乎不一</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:59:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/amid-confused-hamas-statements-israel-says-hostage-talks-continue/00000190-b2e3-d7ee-af9c-ffeb57d40000</guid></item><item><title>拜登和内塔尼亚胡将在以色列总理向国会发表讲话的两天前在白宫会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/biden-netanyahu-to-meet-at-white-house-two-days-before-israeli-pm-addresses-congress/00000190-b285-df47-a7bf-b29f99c90000</link><description>拜登和内塔尼亚胡将于下周举行自美国总统10月7日访问以色列以来的首次会面</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 19:58:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/biden-netanyahu-to-meet-at-white-house-two-days-before-israeli-pm-addresses-congress/00000190-b285-df47-a7bf-b29f99c90000</guid></item><item><title>英国外交大臣访问以色列和约旦河西岸期间呼吁立即停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-07-14/ty-article/.